{
  "stem": "12666.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was so proud that he was using a more efficient gas, Cyclotron C gas, that would kill people quicker than in Treblinka that was not far away.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was so proud that he camouflaged his camp, 'arbeit macht frei,' you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Work makes you free.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he mentioned himself that children were involved, women were involved.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he says, well, we didn't waste anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He says, everything that they had to take off had to be put according to size in a pile.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if they did have any jewelry or anything, we gave them a receipt and took it away.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they had big signs that you have to take showers before you are resettled in the Eastern Territories.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was a story.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So all women, children, and men, they were walked towards the gas chambers, which were camouflaged as shower rooms.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they were locked hermetically in those.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he says, well, before they were locked in those rooms, we cut their hair because the hair had to be used for mattresses.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we knew that they were dead after the cries stopped.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then they had a detail of some inmates who would open the mouth of every victim and take their gold teeth out, put it in special sacks, which they sent to the Reichsbank in Germany.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In fact, when we occupied Germany we found many, many of these sacks with gold teeth that were taken from the victims.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then the victims would be taken to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he says, the bones would not burn, so they had a special machine for grinding bones.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the ashes and what was the grinding bones were used as fertilizer.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
